cac:PartyName.cbc:Name: Department of Housing Local Government and Heritage

cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: Request for Tender for the control of Rhododendron ponticum in Connemara National Park - 2024
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: The Services comprise of the control of Rhododendron ponticum in Connemara National Park divided into 11 Lots. The services are to be completed by 28th February 2025. Pricing for each Lot is to be inclusive of labour and materials. The required approach is Glyphosate application using treatment methods appropriate for local conditions. Further details, including treatment methods, are included in Appendix 1 of this RFT.
